To find the weekly earnings, multiply the daily earnings by the number of days in a week (which typically stands at 7):
Weekly earnings = Daily earnings × Days per week
                       = $1,439,144 × 7
                       ≈ $10,074,008

So, Lloyd makes approximately $10,074,008 per week from the sale of the eggs.
